@startuml component-api-persistence
' ============================================================
' Component Diagram: Backend API and Persistence Layer
' CYO Adventure
'
' Source files:
'   src/cyo_adventure/app.py                 (FastAPI app, middleware order,
'                                              wires all 21 routers)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/health.py          (liveness/readiness/startup probes)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/library.py         (story library endpoints)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/reading.py         (reading-state + completions + series-next)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/generation.py      (guardian-only: concepts, jobs, validate)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/profiles.py        (guardian-only: child profile CRUD)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/families.py        (admin: family listing, create, deactivate)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/ratings.py         (kid ratings)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/assignments.py     (guardian-only: assign storybooks,
'                                              content-summary, catalog /guardian/books)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/approval.py        (global admin: submit/approve/send-back/archive/review)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/covers.py          (AI cover-art request + fetch)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/moderation_thresholds.py (admin: per-band/category
'                                              overrides + noise-floor scalar)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/moderation_dashboard.py  (admin: review surface + suggestions)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/provider_allowlist.py    (admin: provider/model allowlist CRUD)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/me.py              (principal identity)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/story_requests.py  (child request lifecycle: submit,
'                                              list, approve, decline, authored,
'                                              authoring-plan; WS-B)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/child_sessions.py  (mint a child session; guardian/admin
'                                              bearer OR a matching device grant, ADR-014)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/device_grants.py   (ADR-014: mint/list/revoke a device grant)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/onboarding.py      (first-login guardian/admin provisioning)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/admin_users.py     (admin: guardian/admin user mgmt,
'                                              invite/deactivate; WS-J console)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/admin_profiles.py  (admin: cross-family child-profile CRUD)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/family_connections.py (admin: directional cross-family
'                                              recommendation opt-ins)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/schemas.py         (Pydantic request/response models)
'   src/cyo_adventure/api/deps.py            (Principal, Context, auth seam;
'                                              Role.DEVICE routing branch, ADR-014)
'   src/cyo_adventure/core/device_grant.py   (HS256 token, aud cyo-device-grant, 90d)
'   src/cyo_adventure/middleware/correlation.py (CorrelationMiddleware, added first)
'   src/cyo_adventure/middleware/security.py (OWASP headers, SSRF)
'   src/cyo_adventure/core/config.py         (Pydantic Settings)
'   src/cyo_adventure/core/database.py       (async engine, Base, get_session)
'   src/cyo_adventure/core/exceptions.py     (exception hierarchy)
'   src/cyo_adventure/db/models.py           (21 ORM tables)
'   src/cyo_adventure/events/writer.py       (append-only pipeline_event log, WS-D)
'   docs/planning/authorization-matrix.md
'   docs/planning/adr/adr-009-supabase-platform.md (Supabase OIDC replaces Authentik;
'     decision 2 = Supabase Postgres as the operational database)
'   docs/planning/r1-deferred-debt-register.md (Task 1.7: Supabase Postgres cutover;
'     r1-gap-closure-plan.md is archived, consolidated here)
' ============================================================

skinparam defaultFontName "Roboto"
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam componentStyle uml2

skinparam component {
  BorderColor #555555
  FontColor #222222
}

package "FastAPI Application\nsrc/cyo_adventure/app.py" #E8F5E9 {

  package "Middleware Stack (applied first)" #CCEECC {
    component "CorrelationMiddleware\nmiddleware/correlation.py\nAttaches X-Correlation-ID;\nmust be first middleware" as corr_mw #CCEECC
    component "SecurityMiddleware\nmiddleware/security.py\nOWASP headers, HSTS,\nCSP, SSRF protection" as sec_mw #CCEECC
  }

  package "Dependencies\napi/deps.py" #DCEDC8 {
    component "Auth Seam\n_extract_subject()\n[local: token-as-subject]\n[non-local: Supabase OIDC JWT,\nADR-009]" as auth_seam #DCEDC8
    component "Principal\nsubject, user_id, role,\nfamily_id, profile_ids, is_admin\nauthorize_profile() / authorize_family()\n(module-level, take a principal)" as principal #DCEDC8
    component "DbSession\nasync unit-of-work\ncommit on success,\nrollback on exception" as db_session_dep #DCEDC8
    component "RequestContext\nContext = principal + session\nDependency-injected into\nevery route handler" as ctx #DCEDC8
  }

  package "API Routers (20 under /api/v1 + health under /health; 21 total)" #B2DFDB {
    component "health.py\nGET /health/ (root)\nGET /health/live\nGET /health/ready\nGET /health/startup" as health_router #B2DFDB

    component "library.py\nGET /library\n(filtered by age band,\nreading cap, published status)" as library_router #B2DFDB

    component "reading.py\nGET /reading-state/{profile}/{story}\nPUT /reading-state/{profile}/{story}\n(revision-based OCC, idempotent event_id)\nGET /series-next/{profile}/{story}\nPOST /completions" as reading_router #B2DFDB

    component "generation.py [guardian-only]\nPOST /concepts (PII-screened)\nPOST /concepts/{id}/generate\nGET /generation-jobs, /generation-jobs/{id}\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/versions/{v}/validate" as gen_router #B2DFDB

    component "profiles.py [guardian-only]\nGET /profiles\nPOST /profiles\nPATCH /profiles/{id}" as profiles_router #B2DFDB

    component "families.py [admin]\nGET /admin/families\nPOST /admin/families\nPATCH /admin/families/{id}" as families_router #B2DFDB

    component "assignments.py [guardian-only]\nPOST/GET /storybooks/{id}/assignments\nGET /storybooks/{id}/content-summary\nGET /guardian/books (catalog, WS-E)" as assignments_router #B2DFDB

    component "approval.py [global admin]\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/submit\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/approve\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/send-back\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/archive\nGET /storybooks/{id}/review\nGET /review-queue" as approval_router #B2DFDB

    component "covers.py\nPOST /storybooks/{id}/versions/{v}/cover\nGET /storybooks/{id}/versions/{v}/cover" as covers_router #B2DFDB

    component "moderation_thresholds.py [admin]\nGET/PUT/DELETE /admin/moderation-thresholds\nGET/PUT /admin/moderation/noise-floor" as mod_thresh_router #B2DFDB

    component "moderation_dashboard.py [admin]\nGET /admin/moderation/dashboard\nGET /admin/moderation/suggestions" as mod_dash_router #B2DFDB

    component "provider_allowlist.py [admin]\nGET/POST /admin/provider-allowlist\nPUT/DELETE /admin/provider-allowlist/{id}" as allowlist_router #B2DFDB

    component "ratings.py\nPOST /ratings\nGET /ratings/{profile_id}" as ratings_router #B2DFDB

    component "me.py\nGET /me (principal identity)" as me_router #B2DFDB

    component "story_requests.py [WS-B]\nPOST /story-requests\nPOST /story-requests/authored\nGET /story-requests\nPOST /story-requests/{id}/approve\nPOST /story-requests/{id}/decline\nPOST /story-requests/{id}/authoring-plan" as story_req_router #B2DFDB

    component "child_sessions.py\nPOST /child-sessions\n[guardian/admin bearer, OR a\nmatching device grant, ADR-014]" as child_sessions_router #B2DFDB

    component "device_grants.py [ADR-014]\nPOST /device-grants (mint)\nGET /device-grants (list, own family)\nDELETE /device-grants/{id} (revoke)\nGuardian/admin only; never a device token" as device_grants_router #B2DFDB

    component "onboarding.py\nPOST /onboarding\nFirst-login guardian/admin\nprovisioning; refuses child\nsession + device grant tokens" as onboarding_router #B2DFDB

    component "admin_users.py [admin]\nGET /admin/users\nPOST /admin/users (invite, 201)\nPATCH /admin/users/{id}\n(WS-J user management)" as admin_users_router #B2DFDB

    component "admin_profiles.py [admin]\nGET /admin/profiles\nPOST /admin/profiles (201)\nPATCH /admin/profiles/{id}\n(cross-family child profiles)" as admin_profiles_router #B2DFDB

    component "family_connections.py [admin]\nGET /admin/family-connections\nPOST /admin/family-connections (201)\nDELETE /admin/family-connections/{id} (204)" as family_conn_router #B2DFDB
  }

  package "Core" #A5D6A7 {
    component "config.py\nPydantic Settings\nenv vars + .env file\nfails on dev DB in prod" as config #A5D6A7
    component "database.py\nAsync SQLAlchemy engine\nBase ORM class\nget_session() context mgr" as database #A5D6A7
    component "exceptions.py\nValidationError\nResourceNotFoundError\nAuthenticationError\nAuthorizationError\nBusinessLogicError\nProviderError" as exceptions #A5D6A7
  }

}

package "ORM Models\nsrc/cyo_adventure/db/models.py (21 tables)" #FFF8E1 {
  component "Family\nSeries\nUser\nChildProfile\nFamilyConnection\nStorybook\nStorybookVersion" as models_a #FFF8E1
  component "ReadingState\nCompletion\nRating\nStorybookAssignment\nConcept\nStoryRequest" as models_b #FFF8E1
  component "ModerationThreshold(+Audit)\nModerationSetting\nPipelineEvent\nProviderModelAllowlist(+Audit)\nGenerationJob" as models_c #FFF8E1
  component "DeviceGrant [ADR-014]\nfamily_id, authorized_by, jti\n(unique), revoked_at" as models_d #FFF8E1
}

database "Supabase Postgres\n[Managed DB, ADR-009 decision 2]\nAsync SQLAlchemy 2 sessions\nSession pooler :5432 (session mode)\nSupabase CLI SQL migrations (ADR-012)" as pg #E0F7FA

' --- Relationships ---
corr_mw --> sec_mw : "request chain"
sec_mw --> auth_seam : "request chain"
auth_seam --> principal
db_session_dep --> database
principal --> ctx
db_session_dep --> ctx
ctx --> reading_router
ctx --> library_router
ctx --> gen_router
ctx --> health_router
ctx --> profiles_router
ctx --> families_router
ctx --> assignments_router
ctx --> approval_router
ctx --> covers_router
ctx --> mod_thresh_router
ctx --> mod_dash_router
ctx --> allowlist_router
ctx --> ratings_router
ctx --> me_router
ctx --> story_req_router
ctx --> child_sessions_router
ctx --> device_grants_router
ctx --> admin_users_router
ctx --> admin_profiles_router
ctx --> family_conn_router
auth_seam --> onboarding_router : "OnboardingIdentityDep\n(own identity check, not Context:\nno Principal/User row exists yet)"

reading_router --> models_a
reading_router --> models_b
library_router --> models_a
gen_router --> models_a
gen_router --> models_b
gen_router --> models_c
story_req_router --> models_a
story_req_router --> models_b
mod_thresh_router --> models_c
mod_dash_router --> models_c
allowlist_router --> models_c
device_grants_router --> models_d
device_grants_router --> models_a
profiles_router --> models_a
child_sessions_router --> models_a
onboarding_router --> models_a : "creates Family + User\n(first-login provisioning)"
admin_users_router --> models_a : "User/Family mgmt"
admin_profiles_router --> models_a : "ChildProfile CRUD"
family_conn_router --> models_a : "FamilyConnection"

models_a --> pg
models_b --> pg
models_c --> pg
models_d --> pg

exceptions --> reading_router : "raised -> mapped to HTTP\nby exception handlers"
exceptions --> gen_router

note right of auth_seam
  local-only seam: treats bearer token
  as OIDC subject without signature check;
  fails to start outside "local" unless
  OIDC_ISSUER + OIDC_JWKS_URL are set.
  Non-local: _verify_oidc_jwt() validates a
  real Supabase-issued JWT (signature, issuer,
  audience, expiry) via cached JWKS
  (jwt.PyJWKClient), per ADR-009.
  --
  ADR-014 device-grant branch: routes on the
  UNVERIFIED aud claim to
  verify_device_grant_token() (HS256,
  aud=cyo-device-grant, DEVICE_GRANT_SECRET),
  mirroring the existing child-session branch.
  Builds a Role.DEVICE Principal with no
  profile_ids and is_admin force-cleared, so it
  can only ever reach child_sessions_router and
  profiles_router below.
end note

note right of reading_router
  PUT /reading-state uses:
  SELECT ... FOR UPDATE (row lock)
  + state_revision check (OCC)
  + event_id idempotency
  Returns 409 + current row on conflict.
end note

note bottom of gen_router
  Concept/generate/validate endpoints are
  guardian-only (checked before any DB
  access). PII screen on concept creation
  (child display_name must not appear in
  the brief text). Story generation can
  also be enqueued indirectly via
  story_req_router's approve endpoint
  (WS-B), which builds a Concept and
  enqueues a GenerationJob without going
  through POST /concepts.
end note

note bottom of story_req_router
  Approve/decline are guardian-own-family
  or admin-global (404-over-403 existence
  hiding outside scope). Every lifecycle
  transition here also writes a
  PipelineEvent row (events/writer.py,
  WS-D) in the same transaction.
end note

note bottom of family_conn_router
  WS-J admin console (#267): admin_users
  (guardian/admin invite + deactivate),
  admin_profiles (cross-family child
  profiles), and family_connections
  (directional cross-family recommendation
  opt-ins) each write a PipelineEvent
  (USER_MANAGED / FAMILY_MANAGED /
  FAMILY_CONNECTION_CHANGED).
end note

@enduml
